metadata.name: SUPER PEPE 64
metadata.description:
On September 13, 1985, the first Super Mario Bros. was released in Japan for the Famicom, forever changing the face of the gaming industry.
The world's most beloved video game hero in my Pepe 3D version.
Artwork for Super Mario lovers.

Work created in the programs: 3ds max, ZBrush and RedShift.

2K video.
12 seconds of animation.
